
 
Prerequisites:
Minimum component versions:
-	Antimalware client: 4.18.2211.5
-	Engine: 1.1.19900.2
-	Security intelligence: 1.391.345.0
-	Xplat version: 101.23102.* +
-	Sensor/ KB version: >10.8040.*/ March 8, 2022+


Requirements
•	MDE sensors depends on ability of Microsoft Defender Antivirus to scan files and provide information about them.
•	If you are running Microsoft Defender Antivirus as the primary antimalware product on your devices, the Defender for Endpoint agent will successfully onboard.
•	If you are running a third-party antimalware client and use Mobile Device Management solutions or Microsoft Endpoint Manager (current branch), you will need to ensure the Microsoft Defender Antivirus ELAM driver is enabled.







 
